title: BREAKING: WW3 fears as Iran launches ANOTHER missile test JUST DAYS after Trump warning
text:
BREAKING: WW3 fears as Iran launches ANOTHER missile test JUST DAYS after Trump warning BREAKING: WW3 fears as Iran launches ANOTHER missile test JUST DAYS after Trump warning IRAN has ignored President Trump’s warning and launched another lethal ballistic missile test, according to US officials. PUBLISHED: 23:25, Wed, Feb 8, 2017 | UPDATED: 23:44, Wed, Feb 8, 2017 GETTY Iran has launched another set of missile tests 
Although Trump warned Iran that they were “playing with fire”, officials told Fox News that the short-range air missile was released from the same launch pad as the last set of missile tests. 
This latest test comes days after the US placed new sanctions on Iran. 
More to follow...
